text: Nicky, Ricky, Dicky & Dawn is an American comedy television series. It was developed by Michael Feldman and created by Matt Fleckenstein. It premiered on Nickelodeon on September 13, 2014. The series ended on August 4, 2018. It focuses on quadruplets Nicky, Ricky, Dicky, and Dawn Harper, nine years old at the start of the series, who have nothing in common and often fight, but must work together to navigate everyday situations.
